Meet new Sktchy teacher Sena Adjovi!

“From childhood, I have always used and loved graphite,” says Sena, a French/Beninese artist living in Montreal, Canada. “It’s a soft and eerie medium that can also be bold and expressive.”

Sena’s three lessons for 30 Faces/30 Days - Pen & Pencil will focus on slowly building layers to achieve depth, softness and atmosphere in your drawings.

The challenge starts July 1. Learn more/sign up via bio 🔗
